        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         NPCs regen while in combat.  Some regen more than others. Some barely regen at all.  Take Cazel.  He regens very fast even while in combat.  Most mobs, if not all mobs, have greatly increased regen if they are unaggroed Vs aggroed.</P><P><A href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=26159">Reegor</A> Mortees<BR>scaled Warlock<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
