        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Ok, it appears that there is a roughly 15% bonus to damage basically all the time.  Soloing you either have the mob rooted, feared or in melee.  At raids, the mob is in melee with the tanks.  Basically, we've been doing 15% more damage than we thought we would.   Thats pretty significant.  Pyre + Pyro + Splurt is 85 dps by itself on an unmoving mob...</P><P>Daedrea Darksoul<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
